= Machine Learning Process :- The machine learning process involves a series of steps to build, train, and deploy a predictive model from data.
  1. Problem Definition
2. Data Collection
 3. Data Preprocessing
4. Feature Selection/Engineering
 5. Model Selection
6. Model Training
7. Model Evaluation
8. Hyperparameter Tuning
9. Deployment
10. Monitoring and Maintenance

2) Deep Learning Applications in Healthcare
Deep learning, especially neural networks, is revolutionizing healthcare through:
Medical Image Analysis: Detecting tumors in X-rays and MRIs using CNNs
Disease Prediction: Predicting diabetes, heart disease, etc., using EHR data
Drug Discovery: Identifying new drug combinations faster
Personalized Treatment: Tailoring treatment plans using patient-specific data

4) Linear Regression 
Simple Linear Regression models the relationship between one independent variable (X) and one dependent variable (Y).
